WEBVTT

00:00:01.020 --> 00:00:04.430
Hi, I have another dream that the Lord

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:06.410
wanted me to tell you all about.

00:00:06.420 --> 00:00:09.169
Now, this one's pretty

00:00:09.169 --> 00:00:09.179
serious—well,

00:00:09.179 --> 00:00:11.330
all of them have been serious, but this

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:14.690
one was really on my heart this week.

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:19.130
It started out as I was praying over

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:20.390
the wars

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:23.150
and what's going on in Ukraine,

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:27.429
and the Lord showed me a massive storm

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:31.130
on the East Coast of America.

00:00:31.140 --> 00:00:35.389
It was as dark as you could

00:00:35.399 --> 00:00:39.049
see through, like a dark, dark purple

00:00:39.059 --> 00:00:42.709
storm, and the lightning

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:45.290
was striking through it.

00:00:45.290 --> 00:00:45.300
It

00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:46.130
was

00:00:46.140 --> 00:00:48.770
very scary-looking in the natural

00:00:48.780 --> 00:00:52.250
to look at the storm, and it was

00:00:52.260 --> 00:00:56.029
getting closer and closer.

00:00:56.039 --> 00:00:59.630
When I pray, I see in the

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:01.610
spirit and the Lord shows me, and the

00:01:01.620 --> 00:01:03.950
storm gets closer and closer. The last

00:01:03.950 --> 00:01:03.960
time I saw

00:01:03.960 --> 00:01:06.170
it, the rain

00:01:06.170 --> 00:01:06.180
was coming; I

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:08.570
could see

00:01:08.570 --> 00:01:08.580
the

00:01:08.580 --> 00:01:11.090
raindrops

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:12.950
coming out of

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.510
the storm.

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:18.950
But the Lord showed me this massive wall.

00:01:18.950 --> 00:01:18.960
The

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:22.910
wall

00:01:23.580 --> 00:01:27.370
was probably

00:01:27.380 --> 00:01:31.789
five feet thick, maybe more, and

00:01:31.789 --> 00:01:31.799
it

00:01:31.799 --> 00:01:34.130
was made

00:01:34.130 --> 00:01:34.140
of

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:37.130
humongous bricks; it went up as high

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:41.690
as probably thirty feet, or maybe

00:01:41.690 --> 00:01:41.700
even

00:01:41.700 --> 00:01:43.249
bigger, like

00:01:43.249 --> 00:01:43.259
a several-story

00:01:43.259 --> 00:01:44.929
building.

00:01:47.340 --> 00:01:52.010
On this side of it, I could see

00:01:52.020 --> 00:01:54.830
light coming out of

00:01:54.830 --> 00:01:54.840
it.

00:01:54.840 --> 00:01:56.630
The light was shining through the clouds

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:59.929
and it was beautiful. There was a

00:01:59.939 --> 00:02:02.149
stream going through on

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:04.370
this side of the wall, and there was a

00:02:05.939 --> 00:02:09.050
little hut—a little house

00:02:09.060 --> 00:02:11.630
with a picnic table outside of it with

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:14.750
green grass—and there was a

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:17.930
little stove, a chimney

00:02:17.940 --> 00:02:21.890
stove with smoke coming out of

00:02:21.900 --> 00:02:24.050
it, and you could smell the smell of

00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:26.470
bread.

00:02:28.379 --> 00:02:31.309
The Lord told me—I said, "Lord, what is

00:02:31.319 --> 00:02:33.470
this that You're showing me?"—and He said,

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:39.350
"Brandon, this is Psalm 91 and Psalm 23,

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.330
both

00:02:41.330 --> 00:02:41.340
together."He

00:02:41.340 --> 00:02:44.449
said, "If you stay in the secret place

00:02:44.459 --> 00:02:47.570
of the Most High and you abide in that

00:02:47.580 --> 00:02:50.509
shadow of the Almighty, none of that

00:02:50.519 --> 00:02:53.210
storm is going to come near you. But

00:02:53.220 --> 00:02:55.250
you're going to have to stay close to Me

00:02:55.260 --> 00:02:59.210
and get those scriptures, Psalm 91 and

00:02:59.210 --> 00:02:59.220
Psalm

00:02:59.220 --> 00:03:02.930
23, deep down in your heart. It has

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:06.410
to become a Rhema word inside of you for

00:03:06.420 --> 00:03:07.490
what's coming.

00:03:07.500 --> 00:03:11.089
You have to know that word, Psalm 91 and

00:03:11.089 --> 00:03:11.099
Psalm

00:03:11.099 --> 00:03:13.729
23. You can't just read, 'The

00:03:13.739 --> 00:03:15.770
Lord is my shepherd; I shall not

00:03:15.770 --> 00:03:15.780
want.'You

00:03:15.780 --> 00:03:17.809
can't just flippantly echo it by

00:03:17.819 --> 00:03:19.970
just reading it off."You have

00:03:19.980 --> 00:03:22.250
to meditate on the

00:03:22.250 --> 00:03:22.260
pages until

00:03:22.260 --> 00:03:25.130
it becomes a revelation to you and

00:03:25.140 --> 00:03:28.309
gets deep inside your spirit, so

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:31.190
that it is a sword when it comes out of

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:34.550
your mouth. In James

00:03:34.550 --> 00:03:34.560
4:7,

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:37.850
you submit yourself unto God, resist the

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:41.330
devil, and he will flee from you.

00:03:41.340 --> 00:03:43.670
You have to understand that word and

00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:46.070
get a revelation of it, so that when you

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:48.170
are submitting yourself unto God and

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:50.509
resisting the devil, he will flee

00:03:50.519 --> 00:03:52.070
from you. You must have a

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:54.530
revelation of it, because if it's not a

00:03:54.530 --> 00:03:54.540
Rhema

00:03:54.540 --> 00:03:56.690
word inside of you, you might as

00:03:56.700 --> 00:03:58.550
well be singing "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little

00:03:58.550 --> 00:03:58.560
Star,"because

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:00.830
it's not going to have any

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:02.809
power behind it since you're just

00:04:02.809 --> 00:04:02.819
flippantly

00:04:02.819 --> 00:04:05.350
saying things. I can quote

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:08.210
scripture all day long; the devil knows

00:04:08.220 --> 00:04:10.970
the scripture, and he understands the

00:04:10.980 --> 00:04:12.710
scripture better than a lot of

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:15.470
Christians do, but it's whenever the word

00:04:15.480 --> 00:04:18.710
becomes a Rhema to you that it becomes

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:21.650
revelation knowledge that comes out of

00:04:21.660 --> 00:04:24.409
your spirit and becomes powerful. That

00:04:24.409 --> 00:04:24.419
is

00:04:24.419 --> 00:04:26.390
what you need to know: whenever

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:29.570
that word becomes powerful to you, that's

00:04:29.570 --> 00:04:29.580
when

00:04:29.580 --> 00:04:32.870
you're going to get results.

00:04:32.870 --> 00:04:32.880
That

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:34.969
is

00:04:34.979 --> 00:04:36.710
one of the things the Lord told

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:39.050
me to tell you when I was praying this

00:04:39.060 --> 00:04:41.749
morning, so I'm going to end this

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:43.909
video there. I hope you have a blessed

00:04:43.919 --> 00:04:47.210
day. No weapon formed against you

00:04:47.220 --> 00:04:50.090
is going to prosper; you have to get that

00:04:50.100 --> 00:04:51.530
inside of you

00:04:51.540 --> 00:04:53.450
for when the storms are coming.

00:04:54.620 --> 00:04:57.650
Greater is he that is in you than he

00:04:57.660 --> 00:05:01.759
that is in the world. Have a blessed day.

